[SN]TITLE[SN]
Why are some people left-handed?

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
If you prefer to use your left hand, then you're in luck because it's International Left-Handers' Day!

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
13 August 2016 Last updated at 14:23 BST
It's believed that around one in 10 people are left-handed.
But no-one really knows why left-handed people like to use their left hands.
Left-handed Martin's been looking at some of the theories, and how life's not always been easy for lefties...
